_sText:
A map set in the STALKER universe

Background:
An abandoned roadway that is blocked off by debris of old vehicles. A roadside fence that separates you and your opposing team. There are grenade spawners for the teams. The fence in the middle of the map will explode allowing for players to pass over to they other side. The surrounding areas of the map is covered by nature and a vivid look at Chernobyl's story.

Support:
Cubemaps, Grenade_spawners, Overtime ("Guns Spawn"), 48 Spawnpoints

Change Log:
  • None ATM
